<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Experience — Lumina Cafe</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css"/>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="nav">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="logo">LUMINA</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
      <a href="/menu" class="nav-link">Menu</a>
      <a href="/reservations" class="nav-link">Reservations</a>
      <a href="/experience" class="nav-link active">Experience</a>
    </div>
    <button class="mobile-toggle" id="mobileToggle" aria-label="Menu">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Our Story</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">The Experience</h1>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="story-grid">
      <div class="story-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1442512595331-e89e73853f31?w=800" alt="Coffee brewing" loading="lazy"/>
      </div>
      <div class="story-content">
        <span class="section-tag">Our Philosophy</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Where Light <span class="italic">Meets</span> Flavor</h2>
        <p>Lumina Cafe was born from a simple belief: that great food and coffee have the power to bring people together. Founded in 2018, we set out to create a space that feels like an extension of your own home — warm, inviting, and filled with the aromas of something delicious.</p>
        <p>Every drink is crafted with intention. Every dish is prepared with ingredients sourced from local farms and artisans. We believe in sustainability, community, and the quiet beauty of a perfectly poured latte.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section values-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-tag">What We Stand For</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Our <span class="italic">Values</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">&#9733;</div>
        <h3>Quality First</h3>
        <p>We source the finest beans, freshest produce, and highest-quality ingredients. Nothing less than exceptional makes it to your table.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">&#127758;</div>
        <h3>Sustainability</h3>
        <p>From compostable packaging to partnerships with local farms, we're committed to reducing our footprint and nourishing our community.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">&#9749;</div>
        <h3>Craftsmanship</h3>
        <p>Our baristas and chefs are artists. Every drink is poured with precision, every plate plated with care, every guest welcomed with warmth.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="story-grid reverse">
      <div class="story-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554118811-1e0d58224f24?w=800" alt="Cafe interior with warm lighting" loading="lazy"/>
      </div>
      <div class="story-content">
        <span class="section-tag">The Space</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Designed for <span class="italic">Connection</span></h2>
        <p>Our cafe was designed in collaboration with local artisans. The warm wood tones, soft lighting, and open layout create an atmosphere that invites lingering — whether you're catching up with an old friend, diving into a good book, or getting lost in your work.</p>
        <p>We've left space for you to make it your own. Pull up a chair, stay awhile. You're welcome here.</p>
        <a href="/reservations" class="btn btn-primary">Reserve Your Spot</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <h3>LUMINA</h3>
        <p>Light. Flavor. Community.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <h4>Navigate</h4>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/menu">Menu</a>
        <a href="/reservations">Reservations</a>
        <a href="/experience">Experience</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-hours">
        <h4>Hours</h4>
        <p>Mon–Fri: 7am – 9pm</p>
        <p>Sat–Sun: 8am – 10pm</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-contact">
        <h4>Visit</h4>
        <p>42 Elm Street, Downtown</p>
        <p>hello@luminacafe.com</p>
        <p>(555) 123-4567</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Lumina Cafe. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
